handmodel L Oculus_Touch
handmodel R Oculus_Touch

section Laser The laser pointer
state video on

caption .5 .15 3 Each controller has a laser pointer that acts;\
    like the mouse when used with the pinch button
handpoint L CreateSphereIcon 2
click LPinch
wait 1

caption .5 .15 3 It can be used to click or drag, although;\
    pinch dragging can be awkward and imprecise
handpoint R TranslationTool/X/XSlider/MaxFace 1
handmove  R  -.1 0 0  0 -10 0  2 Pinch
wait 1
